# Premium Cinematic Redesign Plan

This plan details the top-to-bottom redesign of the Elite Match application to deliver a "full premium cinematic type" and "high cost" user interface. The goal is to elevate the app into an immersive, editorial-quality experience using a **Pearl White & Rose Gold** aesthetic.

## Proposed Changes

### Global Styles & Layout Layout
Refining the core visual language to feel expensive, light, and atmospheric.

#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///c:/Users/MOHITH%20REDDY/Documents/test-case-elite/apps/web/app/globals.css)
- Update CSS variables for a "Pearl White" background (soft, warm white/cream) and "Rose Gold" primary accents.
- Add advanced utility classes for `ultra-glass` (frosted glass with high blur and subtle white borders), soft dynamic glow effects, and smooth text gradients.
- Refine typography rules for high elegance, utilizing delicate serif headings and crisp sans-serif body text with ample white space.

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/MOHITH%20REDDY/Documents/test-case-elite/apps/web/app/layout.tsx)
- Enhance the background with a subtle, slow-moving animated mesh gradient (soft rose and pearl hues) to create a cinematic, breathing "stage" for the content.
- Change the Next.js `themeColor` and HTML class to support the light premium theme instead of `dark`.

---

### Core Components
Upgrading the building blocks to advanced, interaction-rich components using Framer Motion.

#### [MODIFY] `apps/web/app/components/ui/*.tsx`
- **Button**: Implement magnetic hover effects, shimmer sweeps, press-state scaling, and soft rose gold gradients.
- **Card**: Add tilt-hover effects (using Framer Motion), delicate 1px border gradients, deep soft shadows (neuomorphism/glassmorphism hybrid).
- **Tabs/Navigation**: Redesign with animated floating indicators and subtle frosted glass backdrops.

---

### Key Feature Pages
Transforming standard app layouts into high-end editorial experiences.

#### [MODIFY] [discover/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/MOHITH%20REDDY/Documents/test-case-elite/apps/web/app/(app)/discover/page.tsx)
- **The Swipe Stack**: Make the images larger (edge-to-edge), with a soft vignette gradient overlay from the bottom. 
- **Typography Overlay**: Style the user's name and details like a luxury magazine cover.
- **Interactions**: Smoother physics, haptic-feeling animations, and a glowing auroral effect around the active card based on drag direction (rose gold for like, soft ash/pearl for pass).
- **Actions**: Replace standard buttons with floating, glassmorphic action orbs with soft colored glows.

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run lint -w apps/web` to ensure no Type/Lint errors are introduced.

### Manual Verification
- Start the dev server: `npm run dev`
- Visually inspect the changes in the browser on desktop and mobile viewports.
- Verify framer-motion animations perform smoothly at 60fps.
